nherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1148994&amp;amp;li=17601422&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=04072026&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550" style="display: block !important; width: 100% !important;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普重申了他的最后通牒，要求伊朗同意停火协议并完全重新开放霍尔木兹海峡，否则将面临另一次军事升级。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;昨天，美国总统表示，他并不担心可能犯下&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9-0zMFsSO-lSIL8DTHpECtgiLN9bkJgQ2IklOJ-9UyWVBKIBZa3kzNuCpspVO-ny99-68ygL3MClpzhXyBOlgEvax6uUPIxyZutsLbvuvfdBvexc1q67v5gfU69jAyIF6t4TRjKpvWb07POhG7ZYtB7kUXTDHwfaKwW7hAVQ7NlQ9VLbYYuVvGeLAUsYYy74xyTLcaOLXrdHJVCN080FF55sWwSYTSQt2llEiEQa0C1XAYH2NCJH78GIKKeVNM3YA6BmEIW3jUgwIIBs_Ddmo3hq8_aTZYkrGZf2xMAOqLm5JhMCA9N4z79ih4SF6P_NyM4k2Z-NX0qydrqgJW52TZ1qEQKkLYBK1VJrCJAriDrKiJwaKycYivL5ZzzMVJ-qedwJJPPfIPKwzQAsTB3nppST2lgQxAGPpMmk6ZEPKHl37Id5G-sge8S_5IhuONBQhsY93mzRRugO8YvSqPKt_4Yyvj09gMQVbSevDfr0iVryKPhCiBemaFD1tXvosQCsey92cf4/-sGEb74BcpJNgrxpC6QPdjDNVUTqns-Y/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="联合国警告称，对伊朗基础设施的袭击有违反法律的风险"&gt;战争罪，&lt;/a&gt;因为他承诺摧毁伊朗的民用基础设施，这可能违反了国际法。周二，特朗普更进一步，承诺“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9Yxl_nEulVmuC1nIVm4wEwiKD5_lQgb94kC7z035KxThl9wb8eS7OUO79GvESihzT943DSX_gTatlIf8uUjO06O5MGDszWkKiBhHN1TLy_ZlhNpigJFEQGET_vTDKa8Dy-Sjp2HCfqtCgLnSRT8wPeOfXBtX1hcTIPh4VJy0G_gsCjTd4xLrtswMPzxbooRqMh2-2p9CQ8GFkTQTEke5TBA5hAFJA6iStRynzOejSsr9CdyEtbkBqAmd2yJjDe9_Q0qZ_Ki85NuLNyOFW4qIDGdBgDO9_CniTLWJU21oR4mA_vw5tBnezx5yZqRgYkVImE7xXwM7SwIJtUDPzWHX4FvMGoG9elCraaoZuJS2Iaxiv2dJWtShayNSGMBk3BMVtSXFZYr5_mFSi5VC9Az0DXosLESLJceUrvL69OouGokI9lfBtMmqOG5TJQy6PfAo45osAHtihNxmm3Ej8sz_7ZxiXw2bHyRDdYYVZdC3D6cneBJgRDQffKgEubpvgEz8Z9F2